name: Responsivetabs.GitHub.io
tagline: A simple jquery plugin for responsive tabs
body:
### Responsive Tabs.
A simple plugin developed using jQuery for including responsive tabs in your application. The tabs automatically switch to the select pick list when viewing on the mobile devices(lower screen resolution).
